data.description: Experience the ultimate golf course-front lifestyle in this stunning property that seamlessly combines multiple luxurious elements. Situated beautifully on the WEDGEFIELD golf course, this home offers spectacular GOLF COURSE VIEWS. The entertainment possibilities are endless with a POOL and SPA, and an open layout that includes a FORMAL DINING ROOM, and an OPEN KITCHEN & LARGE FAMILY ROOM.     This well-maintained home boasts - SLIT FLOOR PLAN, TWO-CAR GARAGE, CROWN MOLDING, SCREEN ENCLOSURE, BRICK PAVED PATIO, WATER SOFTENER, and much more! Enjoy the convenience of quick access to SR 50 and SR 528, and be just a short drive from Cocoa Beach, NASA, Walt Disney World, Universal Studios, Sea World, Orlando International Airport, and world-class shopping. Don't miss out on this exquisite Florida golf community home where you can indulge in the perfect blend of luxury and leisure.
